sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Python App
    participant SDK as OpenAI SDK
    participant API as OpenAI API
    participant LLM as GPT-4o

    App->>SDK: chat.completions.create()
    SDK->>API: POST /v1/chat/completions
    API->>LLM: Process prompt
    LLM-->>API: Generated tokens
    API-->>SDK: JSON response
    SDK-->>App: ChatCompletion object

    Note over App,LLM: messages=[{role, content}]
    Note over API,LLM: temperature, max_tokens, model
